OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA little
OL,6,Fshowery rain soon clearing away this
OL,7,Fevening, then dry for a time. Further
OL,8,Fpatchy rain will spread from the west
OL,9,Fin the early hours, then becoming dry
OL,10,Fby the end of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRain will spread northeast for
OL,13,Fa time in the morning, heaviest across
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway. Rather cloudy
OL,15,Fin the afternoon with further rain
OL,16,Fspreading northeast later. Windy in
OL,17,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
